2026-05-12T22:50:09.5630460Z 242        <!--
2026-05-12T22:50:09.5630818Z 243            Override Google Play Billing's ProxyBillingActivity so the system
2026-05-12T22:50:09.5631129Z 244            cannot restore it from Recents or after process death with a
2026-05-12T22:50:09.5631461Z 245            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-12T22:50:09.5631785Z 246            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-12T22:50:09.5631989Z 247            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-12T22:50:09.5632344Z 248            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-12T22:50:09.5632894Z 249            ensures the activity is finished as soon as it leaves the
2026-05-12T22:50:09.5633206Z 250            foreground and is never re-entered with a missing extra. See
2026-05-12T22:50:09.5633525Z 251            crash report tagged "ProxyBillingActivity NPE" for context.
2026-05-12T22:50:09.5633673Z 252        -->
